SNA.js project template

This repository is intended as a JavaScript/TypeScript port of the R package `sna` 2.8.
The original reference source is included under `reference/r-sna-2.8/` for porting only.

Original package metadata:
- Package: sna
- Version: 2.8
- Title: Tools for Social Network Analysis
- Author/Maintainer: Carter T. Butts
- License: GPL (>= 2)
- CRAN publication date in DESCRIPTION: 2024-09-08

Because the intended implementation is a port/derivative of GPL-licensed code, keep this
project under a GPL-compatible license unless you obtain separate permission from the
original copyright holder.
